# Terraform Commands

```bash
terraform fmt
```

Format Terraform code.

```bash
terraform init
```

Initialize providers and modules.

```bash
terraform validate
```

Validate configuration.

```bash
terraform plan
```

Preview changes.

```bash
terraform apply
```

Create infrastructure.

